column5: Recieved the last of the donations today. I would once again ,like to thank you all for your contribution and will be deliverying them personally to Mr. Mercer this weekend. Total recieved was $ 1173.48 .  Thank again,   god bless you all.
Thanks for puttin it together Bud !
It " God bless YOU" Brian. You did a great job....yet again.
